<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pantry Baking - About</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon-pie.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- navbar -->
    <header class="sticky-top">
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    </header>

    <!-- main information -->
    <section class="about-container-section">
        <div class="about-container">
            <h1>About Pantry Baking</h1>
            <p>
                Pantry Baking is a simple recipe website designed to help you bake with what you already have.
                Instead of searching for recipes and realizing you're missing half the ingredients, this site
                lets you filter recipes based on what’s in your pantry or fridge.
            </p>
            <p>
                Just select the ingredients you have, and Pantry Baking will show you recipes you can actually make.
                No extra grocery trips, no wasted time — just practical baking.
            </p>
            <p>
                This project was created as a way to make baking more accessible, flexible, and a little less stressful.
                Whether you're improvising with limited ingredients or just trying to use up what you already own,
                Pantry Baking is here to help.
            </p> 
            <p>
                Happy baking! 🍰
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- footer -->
    <footer>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </footer>

    <script type="module" src="/scripts/recipe.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>